{"id":"6864ce43-3368-4913-b5b0-2e0b221509cf","createdAt":"2026-07-19T04:08:07.269Z","mailboxId":"dffabdfc-3e6c-423e-8feb-fb8c7beae7ca","externalId":"19","from":"\"Manomite Technology\" <gestech11@gmail.com>","to":"services@ziondefi.com","subject":"Hello","text":"How are you doing today\n","html":"<div dir=\"auto\">How are you doing today</div>\n","attachments":[],"messageId":"<CAEH7Ak5ir2YQ4K7bWMzveoi_D9B0g1fyh6YEfhisrNWzSZ72Dg@mail.gmail.com>","inReplyTo":null,"references":[],"receivedAt":{"$$date":1784022451000},"status":"classified","_id":"uqcE9evaAoWG8x68","threat":{"blocked":false,"riskScore":0,"reasons":[],"suspiciousUrls":[],"dangerousAttachments":[],"aiChecked":false,"aiReasoning":null},"updatedAt":"2026-07-19T04:08:15.547Z","classification":{"label":"Uncategorized","confidence":0,"scores":[]},"decision":{"action":"requires_human","confidence":0,"reason":"Confidence (0.00) too low to trust any automated action.","label":"Uncategorized"}}
{"id":"43578d7d-72bb-4eed-97c8-fed2fd99e2ab","createdAt":"2026-07-19T04:08:07.238Z","mailboxId":"dffabdfc-3e6c-423e-8feb-fb8c7beae7ca","externalId":"6","from":"\"Rachael Akalia\" <rachael@yellowcard.io>","to":"services@ziondefi.com","subject":"One platform. Every currency. Complete treasury control.","text":"\nHi Adeyeye,\n\nHere's a snapshot of the payment landscape across emerging markets today:\n\n\tThe average fee to send money across these markets is 8%\n\n\tCross-border transactions can take nearly 5 days to process\n\n\tThe average inflation rate across emerging markets is 10%\n\n\t70% of economies are facing serious FX shortages\n\nFor financial institutions and businesses operating in these environments, these aren't just statistics. They represent trapped capital, unpredictable settlement timelines, FX exposure, and operational costs that compound daily.\n\nThe challenge is that most institutions are still relying on correspondent banking rails and legacy infrastructure that weren't designed for the speed, volume, or complexity of today's emerging market payments.\n\nThis is the problem Yellow Card was built to solve.\n\nOur stablecoin infrastructure enables institutions to:\n\n\tSettle cross-border payments in minutes, not days, with 24/7 availability\n\n\tAccess USD liquidity globally without the need for SWIFT or correspondent bank relationships\n\n\tReduce FX exposure by holding and transacting in USD-pegged stablecoins\n\n\tStreamline multi-currency treasury operations through a single, unified platform\n\nIf your institution is navigating any of these challenges, our team would welcome a short conversation. You can book time directly here:\n\n​​​​\n\nBest,\n\nRachael Akalia\n\nSenior Commercial Marketing Manager\n\nYellow Card\n\n---\n\nYou're receiving this because you submitted an inquiry to Yellow Card. If you'd prefer not to receive updates from us, you can unsubscribe here\n\nhttps://links.yellowcard.io/unsubscribeConfirm/1096833/76cd87a8831e6e9606ac0030ab51c85b6f026fb4e1ccc6202bc09719a451c72e/1674929622\n\n.\n\n\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\"><html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" xml:lang=\"en\" lang=\"en\"><head><meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html;\" /><title>Email Newsletter</title></head><body style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Hi Adeyeye,</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.38; margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-variant: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\">Managing corporate treasury across multiple markets shouldn't mean juggling fragmented systems, chasing settlement confirmations, or losing visibility over your balances.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.38; margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-variant: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\">Yellow Card's Treasury Portal was built to change that.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.38; margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-variant: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\">It's your central command center for corporate treasury, giving your finance and operations teams unified control over fiat and digital assets from a single, intuitive platform.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.38; margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-variant: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\">Here's what that means in practice:</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.38; margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-variant: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\">Unified Control</span></span></span></span><br>\n<span style=\"font-variant: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\">View balances, initiate transactions, and manage both fiat and crypto assets from one place. No more switching between systems or losing time to reconciliation.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.38; margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-variant: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\">Borderless Money Movement</span></span></span></span><br>\n<span style=\"font-variant: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\">Send and receive local fiat, stablecoins, and USD across borders. Manage a multi-currency treasury with seamless conversions between wallets, giving your team the speed and flexibility modern business demands.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.38; margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-variant: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\">Flexible Wallet Custody</span></span></span></span><br>\n<span style=\"font-variant: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\">Create custodial and self-custodial stablecoin wallets for internal treasury management and customer payments. Yellow Card handles all blockchain and stablecoin layers, so your team doesn't have to.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.38; margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:16px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-variant: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\">Whether you're managing multi-currency flows across borders, optimizing your daily settlement, or looking to launch truly borderless financial services, the Treasury Portal gives you the infrastructure to do it without building from scratch.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.38; margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:16px\"><a href=\"https://links.yellowcard.io/e/1096833/LastName-email-Recipient-Email/wrl1vn/1674929622/h/mMI6gNXxHS4ruqKtdOvgd-k_3HTwwsyZ2Daj8ztjtZY\" style=\"color:#1871d8;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-variant: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\">Book a Demo of the Treasury Portal</span></span></span></span></span></span></a><br>\n​​<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">​​​​<br>\n<br>\nBest,<br>\nRachael Akalia<br>\nSenior Commercial Marketing Manager<br>\nYellow Card<br>\n<br>\n---</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">You're receiving this because you submitted an inquiry to Yellow Card. If you'd prefer not to receive updates from us, you can <a href=\"https://links.yellowcard.io/unsubscribeConfirm/1096833/76cd87a8831e6e9606ac0030ab51c85b6f026fb4e1ccc6202bc09719a451c72e/1674929622\" rel=\"nofollow,noreferrer\" style=\"color: #0068A5;\">unsubscribe here</a>.</span></p>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://links.yellowcard.io/r/1096833/1/1674929622/open/1\" /></body></html>\n","attachments":[],"messageId":"<1fbf840e-367d-419e-bc96-09291766905b@iad4s13mta904.xt.local>","inReplyTo":null,"references":[],"receivedAt":{"$$date":1782389399000},"status":"classified","_id":"xBzwOgnwLyeEWnzM","threat":{"blocked":false,"riskScore":0,"reasons":[],"suspiciousUrls":[],"dangerousAttachments":[],"aiChecked":false,"aiReasoning":null},"updatedAt":"2026-07-19T04:08:15.555Z","classification":{"label":"Newsletter","confidence":0.4,"scores":[],"fallback":"ai_unavailable"},"decision":{"action":"archive","confidence":0.4,"reason":"Newsletter content is routed to the Newsletter Intelligence Agent and archived.","label":"Newsletter"}}
