{"id":"05889865-2c1c-45c0-99c5-096fbad8d52c","createdAt":"2026-07-19T04:14:10.717Z","mailboxId":"dffabdfc-3e6c-423e-8feb-fb8c7beae7ca","externalId":"31","from":"\"Zion Matrix\" <zionmatrixhq@gmail.com>","to":"services@ziondefi.com","subject":"Re: Purchasing software","text":"Okay thats great lets make it $75\n\nOn Sun, 19 Jul 2026, 05:13 , <services@ziondefi.com> wrote:\n\n> Subject: Proposal to Purchase License\n>\n> Dear [Recipient's Name],\n>\n> I hope this message finds you well. I am writing to express my interest in\n> purchasing a license for your product/service.\n>\n> As discussed, the standard price is $100. In consideration of this\n> purchase, I would like to propose acquiring the license at a 10% discount —\n> that is, for $90.\n>\n> Please let me know if this arrangement is acceptable or if you’d like to\n> discuss next steps. I’m happy to move forward promptly upon your\n> confirmation.\n>\n> Best regards,\n> [Your Name]\n>\n","html":"<div dir=\"auto\">Okay thats great lets make it $75</div><br><div class=\"gmail_quote gmail_quote_container\"><div dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gmail_attr\">On Sun, 19 Jul 2026, 05:13 , &lt;<a href=\"mailto:services@ziondefi.com\">services@ziondefi.com</a>&gt; wrote:<br></div><blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\">Subject: Proposal to Purchase License  <br>\n<br>\nDear [Recipient&#39;s Name],  <br>\n<br>\nI hope this message finds you well. I am writing to express my interest in purchasing a license for your product/service.  <br>\n<br>\nAs discussed, the standard price is $100. In consideration of this purchase, I would like to propose acquiring the license at a 10% discount — that is, for $90.  <br>\n<br>\nPlease let me know if this arrangement is acceptable or if you’d like to discuss next steps. I’m happy to move forward promptly upon your confirmation.  <br>\n<br>\nBest regards,  <br>\n[Your Name]<br>\n</blockquote></div>\n","attachments":[],"messageId":"<CAO